title: Tom Daley posts picture of his engagement rings on Instagram
text:
Tom Daley posts picture of his engagement rings on Instagram Tom Daley posts picture of his engagement rings on Instagram 
Press Association 2014 / / National Entertainment News Share 
Tom Daley has shown off his and partner Dustin Lance Black’s new engagement rings in a beautiful Instagram shot. 
The Olympic bronze medal-winning diver announced his engagement to the filmmaker in the Times’ Birth, Marriages and Deaths section on Thursday. 
In the snap, posted on Friday morning, the pair’s silver engagement rings were placed artfully on top of the newspaper announcement. 
It read: “The engagement is announced between Tom, son of Robert and Debra Daley of Plymouth, and Lance, son of Jeff Bisch of Philadelphia and Anne Bisch of Lake Providence.” (Ian West/PA) Share article 
Tom, 21, has dated Lance, 20 years his senior, for nearly two years, and came out as gay in a YouTube video in December 2013. Promoted Stories
